==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tramway
<hw>Tram"way`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Same as
<er>Tramroad</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A street railway laid in the streets of a town or
city, or an interurban railway for local traffic, on which cable cars,
or trolley cars, etc., are used, in distinction from an extended railway
line for trains drawn by steam or electric locomotives.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tranation</ent>⟦br⟧
